00:34:53,800 --> 00:34:54,630
Lao Wen,

547
00:34:57,150 --> 00:35:00,190
you and my master

548
00:35:01,120 --> 00:35:02,600
are master-and-disciple in name only,

549
00:35:04,470 --> 00:35:05,710
If you don't want to acknowledge
 that the Four Seasons Manor

